727628f-a.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 195th Street
727628f-a.text:
Northern Boulevard, north side, between 195th and 196th
Streets, showing the T.H. Willitts Mansion. In 1891 the
Willetts property comprised 106 acres extendirg north to
Crocheron Avenue.
